{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/G_04_12fps.gif?t=1738047943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A post-apocalyptic point &amp; click adventure in first person view.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore and investigate desolate places in a swampy wasteland.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/G_03_12fps.gif?t=1738047943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When a path is available, an arrow appears as soon as the mouse hovers over it. You can click on it to navigate to next scene. When it is a magnifying glass, it indicates a detailed point of view.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some objects are pickable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/G_01_15fps.gif?t=1738047943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the right combination of objects by dropping them on elements of the scene to trigger animated sequences.<br> Keep on your investigation to unravel the mystery of the mutant plague.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/G_02_12fps.gif?t=1738047943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can combine items in inventory when appropriate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Special attention has been paid to creating an atmospheric immersive experience with sounds.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738047943","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738047943","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/6722cfe3a25190